{"tid":2418149,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解一定要睇狂舞派3","createTime":"2021-02-22T11:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T04:41:34.000Z","uid":335530,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c75aa6dc4dcbc2ab88edfbb4e2943c6d23fad03","tid":2418149,"uid":335530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:42:28.000Z","msg":"眼見幻愛開左幾十個po 狂舞派竟然得個零頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想大家支持下狂舞派3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一 支持本土電影<br />\n<br />\n黃修平老早係14年已經表左態 字幕仲用廣東話字幕 係真正既本土電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二 有共鳴<br />\n<br />\n狂舞派3入面講地產霸權 宣揚保衛家園 如果你有支持幻愛咁點可以唔支持狂舞派3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三 演員班底 <br />\n<br />\n除左第一集既演員之外仲有heyo等香港人 唔係黎黎去去都古天樂 張家輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四 首主題曲太撚正<br />\n<br />\n直接貼link<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gwrRmAuWzQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgwrRmAuWzQw&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XjrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=bb6aaf0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gwrRmAuWzQw</a><br />\n<br />\n聽到後面真係起雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Pd3JuQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Pd3JuQ.png&h=14d5a882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同期既電影市場好大 但狂舞派3個市場就只有香港 所以希望大家支持下本土電影 呢套本土色彩好鮮明 可能聽日就被打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n仲可以loop埋首歌 spotify都上左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後貼段歌詞<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">舉起拳頭 我哋就話比你哋知 <br />\n我哋就係代表住呢一個城市 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"1bc4dcef1faaf934240c06cf4d203087286a9ef7","tid":2418149,"uid":115169,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:12:59.000Z","msg":"因為幻愛嘅歷史以來最出色嘅電影 超越kubrick，Ingmar同黑澤明所有電影，邊個話唔好睇 邊個就係冚家產！"},{"pid":"115ed46dca29f36e0ec8f528dc9591da023fcd4f","tid":2418149,"uid":110939,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已入場。一直都好中意Heyo 唱rap。"},{"pid":"04f1b9b8f1581baef57bb734efe080b72a89fed2","tid":2418149,"uid":157994,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"咪又係工廈音樂狗<br />\n成班廢青嘈生哂"},{"pid":"e5c8a438a15f73e87fca2d1fd977ed47e29f0918","tid":2418149,"uid":142403,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇咗，比上一集更有故事性，我原本對hip hop , rap麻麻，睇完有改觀，rap真係好講技巧。睇完全場唔走睇晒個<br />\nroller,香港少有，點知roller完，演員同導演仲出場同觀眾傾吓偈，戲院細兼只賣半數位，就算滿晒觀眾人數都唔多，但佢哋都仲好努力出嚟同大家見吓面，淨係咁都已值得支持。利申:近日睇咗Nomadland,但我enjoy呢套多D，因為就係本士出產嘅港產片，睇到好多熟識嘅街景同人物。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMHemMB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMHemMB.jpg&h=9fc9cad0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f242bbde16096a1d157a3329e915bdab73ffb134","tid":2418149,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a9261d2f4aa1afb79460a5f91dbf83788cedc6d","tid":2418149,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"個班底真係太差"}]}